{"tid":1244780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[621反思]各位發夢香港621贏到既請入黎","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:39:52.000Z","uid":57274,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e80a03f627cd4c9f8d5b6d3631f6a422797f9b0","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"知道大家都集氣等死線<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日五點</span></span>，如政府唔回應四大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- 撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n- 釋放被捕義士<br />\n- 撤銷612暴動定性<br />\n- 追究警察濫用暴力</span><br />\n<br />\n就會係聽日<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">21號朝早七點</span></span>各自行動升級，逼政府正面回應及作出行動。<br />\n<br />\n但琴晚發夢夢見金鐘得返小貓幾隻，對聽日會出黎既人數仍然有憂慮，亦引申出對21號行動既反思同bug，希望拎出黎討論下。<br />\n<br />\n先不說民陣推71遊行，部分人滿足於616既二百萬人遊行，621行動係自發性，政府而家擺出低姿態，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>由616當日開始採取溫和政策不設警方防線，又宣佈明日大嶼及國歌二讀將押後至下個立法年度，擺明就係想香港人丟淡612既策略</strong></span></span>，配合埋616當日既歡樂氣氛，有一部份人可能都會袋住先正常返工生活。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地點都要預定621未必有足夠既群眾人數去支援義士行動升級。<br />\n（當然希望有咁多傳媒coverage到時都會有接近之前既人數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n假設21號會出黎既人數少，係咪都會升級行動？如意思係狗不動，我不動，最終既行動會係點？同佢地鬥企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如警方保持溫和策略，不設防線又絕不出手，升級行動會否失民意？<br />\n假設21號會出黎既人數比之前人數相若或更多，係咪都係狗不動，我不動？有冇一個終極行動？<br />\n<br />\n再說明日大嶼已押後，聽日日頭行動理由不充分，夜晚立法會更收曬工，<br />\n鑑於之前發夢都係邊退邊守，冇一個最後行動既定案，又唔知真係會行動既義士有幾多，外圍既形勢已經對我地不利下，小弟覺得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有組織既行動都幾重要，唔係就變鳩做同令勇武失民意</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講完手段，到目的。唔係鼓吹<del>勝利氣氛</del>（<span style=\"color: red;\">由一開始103萬人上街都冇理過你就知一直都輸緊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但理性啲睇，777應該唔會係今個立法年度再推逃犯條例，亦係溫水煮蛙既策略黎，試完水溫先日後再部署點繞道通過。<br />\n<br />\n咁眼前最重要既係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放人</span></span>、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平反暴動</span></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">濫用警力</span></span>。雖然列左四項訴求，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>實際想得到既成果一直都好似唔夠清晰</strong></span>，要求政府立刻放人？不檢舉？暴動其實只係字眼，而777同盧偉聰都只係不斷推波同兜圈，最緊要係被捕義士不能以參與暴動罪名被檢控。追究警察濫用暴力其實要直接動搖投訴機制或監警會先有可能達到。<br />\n<br />\n唔係消極主義，本身十分認同支持此四項訴求，亦銘記於心離世烈士既遺願，<br />\n但現實啲去諗，政治活動終歸政治，要考慮成本同收益，即是話，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係政府讓最大步既情況下，今次反逃犯條例行動究竟可以爭取到幾多實質成果？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n行動固然重要，但如果一直拖落去，人力消耗，民意消耗，方向散亂，最終今次運動都係會不了了之，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以大家要諗定，去到邊個位要收手，然後趁有籌碼時攞走最多既成效，而邊啲成效係重要又可取。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟愚見，其實好多群眾都係因為612既警方暴力同烈士犧牲後出去，如不想行動無疾而終，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>教育及宣傳戰應由警方使用過分武力著手</strong></span>，即時開展，如現正搞緊既社區放映，不斷回帶當日荒謬情形，亦預防香港人太快淡忘，覺得社會如常安穩的虛構感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後話：<br />\n再睇長遠啲，香港已俾人揸住碌jer太耐，只係今次又剛好有個時機揭起一直存在既殘酷事實，就連外資都因為而家中共既全面干預而考慮緊徹資，<span style=\"color: red;\">可以點樣令香港有籌碼唔俾中共對香港任意妄為既意識十分重要，亦係需要散播既長期抗爭意識－</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地冇勝利過，係而家呢個俾中共掌控既極權港府下，我地極力抗爭都只係得到呢個政府拖延既安慰劑，我地要得到成效但係係得到真正自由前絕不妥協，每次抗爭都不是勝利，只係龜速地還原應有面貌。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Tx5jTYKIBKE/VWvCCDMB03I/AAAAAAAAGWw/VH4ig9E0_R8/s1600/4bd820ea74b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Tx5jTYKIBKE%2FVWvCCDMB03I%2FAAAAAAAAGWw%2FVH4ig9E0_R8%2Fs1600%2F4bd820ea74b6f.jpg&h=bbaff196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee6069b98aaf8283fc5faa1200f547e12c85703","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359e0e6fc46fb4f5780a2c6082499734135a2323","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285bb83c13bc15578ae5a014992014d927f4bcff","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035c15900c78f0cb54bc68b64349baafa7e483b2","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ac12e3dd9f6e206d98b1853d9d3e7a2715d19e","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32e849cfb1e89bf4741ecf18b14d637f0b05550","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"出面個個都講緊類似問題<br />\n冇人討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8c1cde7a21c4301f5d843ce895e4aa96e9b33e","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde0d4d9c0ec1ab0339e8fb83fd4c904289706ca","tid":1244780,"uid":13098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"推 難得好post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1abeb635fac433850ee8672a55b8009114eb3d","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9b7d184d5e579ccad6f246694291849a62e43f","tid":1244780,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"[621]人數與行動的關係<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244761</a><br />\n推，的確要部署定萬一621失敗嘅反續行動"},{"pid":"1752f62ece36b1d5fcd6c39d793db52ba238bfd1","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b9b7d184d5e579ccad6f246694291849a62e43f","tid":1244780,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"[621]人數與行動的關係<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244761</a><br />\n推，的確要部署定萬一621失敗嘅反續行動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"[拋磚引玉] 6.21 不合作/超合作行動 癱瘓政府 分化內部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243963</a><br />\n<br />\n不合作運動係諗得過，但要一般民眾去做，而家先做宣傳會唔會太遲？<br />\n如果得返好似巴打講幾千人，再拖落去係咪得返消耗？<br />\n如失敗，我覺得不斷做返左膠野教育同散播最緊要，<br />\n針對警力過大，回帶狗狗濫用暴力，keep住民憤，亦藉此維持社會並不安寧既事實，繼而質疑政權既合法性。<br />\n最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要散播每次抗爭都未勝利既思想"},{"pid":"a6e5ab70b3d868176706e21e36f10900e0331001","tid":1244780,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"點先為之唔夠人先。<br />\n<br />\n幾千人夠唔夠？"},{"pid":"dcb38cbe4c8dce4ab0ec28623e2a70814033a2e7","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6e5ab70b3d868176706e21e36f10900e0331001","tid":1244780,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"點先為之唔夠人先。<br />\n<br />\n幾千人夠唔夠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"幾千人當然唔夠<br />\n一黎冇籌碼<br />\n一齊俾狗圍就收皮<br />\n而得幾千人既行動都唔會有民意授權<br />\n所以要考慮下如果人數唔夠<br />\n行動是否繼續 想達到咩目標"},{"pid":"c366d4dd19c6837b2ec0d72530edfd342596db01","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6e5ab70b3d868176706e21e36f10900e0331001","tid":1244780,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"點先為之唔夠人先。<br />\n<br />\n幾千人夠唔夠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"69當日發夢深夜得幾千人大家都係得個退字<br />\n然後逼出灣仔後狗包抄就分段逼散人潮<br />\n遂步散去<br />\n若非仲有612<br />\n應不了了之"},{"pid":"b3388b2d330d38b0273d20f0dc420865bd2c3b93","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efeebd715aba1de4f88be432074ca8b3601ed56","tid":1244780,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed7df8e45862870743ea1d9cdf81e4f0435c7d6","tid":1244780,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91f90508b7c0b505d6a59fec310f2c3509681438","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050fd43c756ea445eecb652f56e0c238c9891a37","tid":1244780,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"【繼續吹】我地只係步緊黃背心後塵！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cQNaRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cQNaRS</a>"},{"pid":"933e7062c7ffcbd911d1ec12faa22759f1cc434d","tid":1244780,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d838d8dc7f9a82c70e91ac5b6ed527c41072f6dd","tid":1244780,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0277d5bd87d84b57ed3fe4046c5db8e396e23d42","tid":1244780,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}